<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="popular-scholarship-programs-in-turkey">Popular Scholarship Programs in Turkey</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">The most popular scholarship programs for foreign students in Turkey are run by three main institutions. Each addresses different fields and application criteria. The table below compares these scholarships and the support they offer:</p>


