<p class="wp-block-paragraph">If you&#8217;re thinking of studying at a university in Turkey and you&#8217;ve set your sights on Özyeğin University, one of the first things you&#8217;re probably wondering is: How much does Ozyegin University Education Fees cost? And you&#8217;re not wrong, because cost planning is really at the forefront of everything for students coming from abroad.</p>



