<td>$22,000</td>
</tr>
</thead>
</table>
</figure>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">As of 2025, Özyeğin University tuition fees are set at approximately <strong>US$22,000</strong> per year for undergraduate programs. This fee applies to most departments, from engineering to business, social sciences to design. However, some programs have special pricing. For example:</p>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li><strong>Professional Flight Program:</strong> The training fee is $14,300 per year. But it doesn&#8217;t end there. You also have to pay <strong>73,500 Euros + VAT</strong> for mandatory flight training, which is not included in the annual fee. Moreover, this program <strong>does not offer scholarships</strong>.</li>



<li><strong>Preparatory Program:</strong> If you are not proficient in English, you will need to take preparatory education. The fee for this program is the same as the undergraduate program, so it is included in the list of Özyeğin University Tuition Fees.</li>
</ul>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Keep in mind that these fees are for education only. In other words, expenses such as dormitory, food and transportation are not included in this. The annual living expenses of an average international student in Istanbul can easily reach several thousand dollars.</p>


<div style="height:23px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity" >
<div style="height:23px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>


<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="payment-options-and-installment-facilities">Payment Options and Installment Facilities</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Özyeğin University Tuition Fees do not have to be paid in one lump sum. The university offers flexible payment options to ease the financial burden of students. Payment methods for the 2025-2026 academic year are both easy and secure.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="online-and-bank-payment">Online and Bank Payment</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">You can pay your fees through the <a href="https://www.ozyegin.edu.tr/tr/ogrenci-hizmetleri/ucretler-ve-odemeler/odeme-yontemleri" target="_blank" rel="noopener">official payment system</a> by:</p>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li>Pay Online with Credit Card or Debit Card</li>



<li>Pay with VakifBank Vinov Campus</li>



<li>Cash Payment at Fibabanka Branches</li>
</ul>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">The accessibility of these methods for international students is a great advantage. You do not need to open an account in Turkey and others can make payments on your behalf.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="installment-options">Installment Options</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Ozyeğin University Tuition Fees are usually paid in <strong>two installments</strong>:</p>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li><strong>1st Installment:</strong> Beginning of the fall semester</li>



<li><strong>2nd installment:</strong> Beginning of spring semester</li>
</ul>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">For example, here is the payment plan for a student who wins a 50% scholarship:</p>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li><strong>Discounted Fee:</strong> 11,000 USD</li>



<li><strong>Prepayment:</strong> 1,000 USD</li>



<li><strong>1st Installment (Fall):</strong> 4,500 USD</li>



<li><strong>2nd Installment (Spring):</strong> 5,500 USD</li>
</ul>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">This structure greatly reduces the pressure on Özyeğin University Tuition Fees. All payment dates are published in the academic calendar; you should definitely follow this calendar because late payment may cause problems in registration.</p>


<div style="height:23px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity" >
<div style="height:23px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>


<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="reducing-education-costs-with-scholarship-opportunities">Reducing Education Costs with Scholarship Opportunities</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">If you are worried about your budget but still want to study at Özyeğin, there is good news: you have a good chance of getting a scholarship. These scholarships, which have a direct impact on Özyeğin University Tuition Fees, are awarded based on both academic achievement and personal profile.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="it-is-not-necessary-to-apply-for-scholarships">It is not necessary to apply for scholarships</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">When you submit your application, you are automatically considered for a scholarship. You do not need to fill out an additional form. The university&#8217;s scholarship system is one of the most comprehensive among foundation universities in Turkey.</p>


<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="scholarship-and-tuition-credit-options-2025-yili-icin-nelerdir">


<p class="wp-block-paragraph">What are the Scholarship and Tuition Loan Options for 2025?</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">In 2025, Özyeğin University offers different scholarship options for international students.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph"><strong>Full Scholarship:</strong> Students with high academic achievement are offered full scholarships covering the entire tuition fee.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph"><strong>50% and 25% Scholarships:</strong> Partial scholarships are available for applicants with a good GPA. These scholarships are automatically evaluated at the time of application.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph"><strong>If you are curious about the application process, evaluation criteria and which documents are effective, be sure to check out our article <a href="https://roadtostudy.com/en/ozyegin-university-scholarship/" data-type="post" data-id="5013">Özyeğin University Scholarship Application 2025: Don&#8217;t Miss Your Chance</a>.</strong> There we explained all the steps of the process in detail.</p>


<div style="height:23px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity" >
<div style="height:23px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>


<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="studying-at-ozyegin-may-be-more-convenient-than-you-think">Studying at Ozyegin may be more convenient than you think</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Many international students are hesitant at first because of Özyeğin University tuition fees. But the truth of the matter is that these fees become much more manageable thanks to scholarship opportunities, installment payment plans, and standard pricing regardless of the department.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">The most important point to remember when thinking about Ozyegin University Tuition Fees is this: the quality of the education you receive, the campus facilities and the experience of living in a city like Istanbul add value far beyond this cost.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">The decision is yours. But if you want to get a world-class education in Turkey, Özyeğin University Tuition Fees may not be the obstacle to your dream. Maybe you just need to take the first step.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Now is the time. Don&#8217;t postpone your dream, take action. As <a class="" href="https://roadtostudy.com">Road to Study</a>, we are with you every step of the way.</p>', '$.wp_published_at', '2025-07-21T13:40:21Z', '$.wp_modified_at', '2026-03-15T18:52:45Z', '$.featured_image', json('{"provider":"external","src":"/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/ozyegin-university-education-fees.webp","alt":"Özyeğin University Tuition Fees and Pay Options","title":"ozyegin-university-education-fees"}')) WHERE "collection" = 'posts' AND "id" = ( SELECT "live_revision_id" FROM "ec_posts" WHERE "deleted_at" IS NULL AND "status" = 'published' AND "locale" = 'en' AND "slug" = 'ozyegin-university-education-fees' );
