ideo is-provider-youtube wp-block-embed-youtube wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper">
<iframe loading="lazy" title="Özyeğin University 2020" width="720" height="405" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/yH3rYaDDUtE?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe>
</div></figure>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Ozyeğin University faculties, one of Istanbul&#8217;s innovative foundation universities, offer a wide range of education for students with different academic interests. In this article, we discuss in detail the faculties, departments, master&#8217;s degree opportunities and advantages for international students.</p>


<div style="height:23px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity" >
<div style="height:23px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>


<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="faculties-and-departments-whats-in-which-area">Faculties and Departments: What&#8217;s in Which Area?</h2>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="faculty-of-business-administration">Faculty of Business Administration</h3>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li>Business</li>



<li>Economy</li>



<li>Entrepreneurship</li>



<li>International Finance</li>



<li>International Trade and Business Management</li>



<li>Management Information Systems</li>
</ul>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="faculty-of-engineering">Faculty of Engineering</h3>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li>Computer Engineering</li>



<li>Electrical-Electronics Engineering</li>



<li>Industrial Engineering</li>



<li>Civil Engineering</li>



<li>Mechanical Engineering</li>



<li>Mathematics Engineering</li>



<li>Artificial Intelligence and Data Engineering</li>
</ul>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="faculty-of-social-sciences">Faculty of Social Sciences</h3>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li>Psychology</li>



<li>International Relations</li>



<li>Antropology</li>



<li>Human and Social Sciences</li>
</ul>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="faculty-of-aviation-and-space-sciences">Faculty of Aviation and Space Sciences</h3>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li>Aviation Management</li>



<li>Pilotage</li>
</ul>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="faculty-of-law">Faculty of Law</h3>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li>Law</li>
</ul>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="faculty-of-architecture-and-design">Faculty of Architecture and Design</h3>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li>Architecture</li>



<li>Industrial Design</li>



<li>Communication and Design</li>



<li>Interior Architecture and Environmental Design</li>
</ul>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="faculty-of-applied-sciences">Faculty of Applied Sciences</h3>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li>Gastronomy and Culinary Arts</li>



<li>Hotel Management</li>
</ul>


<div style="height:23px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity" >
<div style="height:23px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>


<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="the-featured-areas-of-each-faculty">The Featured Areas of Each Faculty</h2>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li><strong>Faculty of Business:</strong> Focus on entrepreneurship, finance and management.</li>



<li><strong>Faculty of Engineering:</strong> A broad engineering background, from artificial intelligence to industrial systems.</li>



<li><strong>Faculty of Law:</strong> A program with a vision of international law, enriched with up-to-date content.</li>



<li><strong>Faculty of Architecture and Design:</strong> Sustainability and aesthetic-oriented design approach.</li>



<li><strong>Faculty of Aeronautics and Astronautics:</strong> It draws attention with its pilotage training, which is one of the few in Turkey.</li>



<li><strong>Faculty of Social Sciences:</strong> Opportunity for in-depth analysis in departments such as psychology and international relations.</li>



<li><strong>Faculty of Applied Sciences:</strong> It stands out with applied trainings such as gastronomy and hotel management.</li>
</ul>


<div style="height:23px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity" >
<div style="height:0px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<div style="height:23px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>


<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="the-road-from-engineering-to-gastronomy">The Road from Engineering to Gastronomy</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Özyeğin University Engineering departments offer not only theoretical but also practical content supported by sectoral projects.<br>Applied departments such as Gastronomy provide practical training in fully equipped kitchens in real restaurant environments.</p>



<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="law-psychology-and-international-trade-departments">Law, Psychology and International Trade Departments</h2>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li><strong>Faculty of Law</strong>: Lessons enriched with current events and case studies</li>



<li><strong>Psychology</strong>: Practices for both individual and social mental health</li>



<li><strong>International Trade and Business</strong>: Preparing for the global market</li>
</ul>



<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="gain-academic-depth-with-institutes">Gain Academic Depth with Institutes</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">There are three main institutes for students considering graduate studies:</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="institute-of-science">Institute of Science</h3>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li>Artificial Intelligence</li>



<li>Data Science</li>



<li>Mathematics</li>
</ul>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="institute-of-social-sciences">Institute of Social Sciences</h3>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li>Psychology</li>



<li>International Relations</li>



<li>Design</li>
</ul>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="institute-of-business">Institute of Business</h3>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li>MBA (Master of Business Administration)</li>



<li>EMBA (Executive MBA)</li>



<li>Financial Engineering</li>
</ul>


<blockquote class="wp-block-quote">


<p class="wp-block-paragraph"><strong>Note:</strong> For master&#8217;s degree application requirements, please visit <a class="" href="https://www.yok.gov.tr" target="_blank" rel="noopener">YÖK Official Website</a>.</p>


</blockquote>
<div style="height:23px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity" >
<div style="height:23px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>


<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="advantageous-options-for-international-students">Advantageous Options for International Students</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Özyeğin University offers international students a strong academic and social environment with its multicultural character.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph"><strong>Real Student Experience:</strong><br>One of the international students studying at Ozyegin University shares her experience as follows:</p>



<figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-youtube wp-block-embed-youtube wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper">
<iframe loading="lazy" title="International Student Testimonials - Pakistan" width="720" height="405" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/uMrQJrLf0A0?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe>
</div></figure>

<div class="wp-block-spacer" style="height: 47px;" aria-hidden="true"> </div>


<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="english-education-programs">English Education Programs</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">The following sections are presented entirely in English:</p>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li>Business</li>



<li>Computer Engineering</li>



<li>International Trade</li>



<li>Pilotage</li>



<li>Psychology</li>
</ul>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">It is also possible to study in Europe through overseas exchange programs such as Erasmus+ and double diploma.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="scholarship-opportunities">Scholarship Opportunities</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Scholarships ranging from 25% to 100% are available for international students. These scholarships are usually awarded based on academic achievement and are evaluated at the time of application without requesting additional documents.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph"><strong>For scholarship types, application requirements and detailed information:</strong><br><br><a class="" href="https://roadtostudy.com/ozyegin-universitesi-burs/">Özyeğin University Scholarship Guide</a>, be sure to check our page.</p>


<div style="height:23px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity" >
<div style="height:23px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>


<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="academic-and-social-supports">Academic and Social Supports</h2>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li><strong>Orientation Programs</strong>: Helps new students adapt to the campus and Istanbul</li>



<li><strong>Social Clubs and Activities</strong>: Seminars, communities supporting personal development</li>



<li><strong>Internship and Project Opportunities</strong>: A chance to step into the industry without graduating</li>
</ul>


<div style="height:23px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity" >
<div style="height:23px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>


<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="now-its-your-turn">Now It&#8217;s Your Turn!</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Ozyeğin University is a university that provides vision as well as knowledge.<br>Take a look at our <a class="" href="https://roadtostudy.com">Road to Study</a> page and start the application process now to get one step closer to your dream career.</p>', "wp_published_at" = '2025-07-22T10:07:27Z', "wp_modified_at" = '2026-03-15T18:52:41Z', "featured_image" = '{"provider":"external","src":"/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/ozyegin-universitesi-faculties-and-schools.webp","alt":"Özyeğin University campus and faculties building","title":"ozyegin-universitesi-faculties-and-schools"}' WHERE "deleted_at" IS NULL AND "status" = 'published' AND "locale" = 'en' AND "slug" = 'ozyegin-university-faculties';
