<li><strong>Faculty of Engineering:</strong> A broad engineering background, from artificial intelligence to industrial systems.</li>



<li><strong>Faculty of Law:</strong> A program with a vision of international law, enriched with up-to-date content.</li>



<li><strong>Faculty of Architecture and Design:</strong> Sustainability and aesthetic-oriented design approach.</li>



<li><strong>Faculty of Aeronautics and Astronautics:</strong> It draws attention with its pilotage training, which is one of the few in Turkey.</li>



<li><strong>Faculty of Social Sciences:</strong> Opportunity for in-depth analysis in departments such as psychology and international relations.</li>



<li><strong>Faculty of Applied Sciences:</strong> It stands out with applied trainings such as gastronomy and hotel management.</li>
