</ul>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">It is also possible to study in Europe through overseas exchange programs such as Erasmus+ and double diploma.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="scholarship-opportunities">Scholarship Opportunities</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Scholarships ranging from 25% to 100% are available for international students. These scholarships are usually awarded based on academic achievement and are evaluated at the time of application without requesting additional documents.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph"><strong>For scholarship types, application requirements and detailed information:</strong><br><br><a class="" href="https://roadtostudy.com/ozyegin-universitesi-burs/">Özyeğin University Scholarship Guide</a>, be sure to check our page.</p>


