 Turkey","publisher":{"@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/#person"},"inLanguage":"en-US"},{"@type":"ImageObject","@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/ozyegin-universitesi-scholarship-tours.webp","url":"https://roadtostudy.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/ozyegin-universitesi-scholarship-tours.webp","width":"1024","height":"604","caption":"Types of scholarships offered at Özyeğin University","inLanguage":"en-US"},{"@type":"WebPage","@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/en/ozyegin-equal-opportunity-in-education/#webpage","url":"https://roadtostudy.com/en/ozyegin-equal-opportunity-in-education/","name":"Ozyegin University 2025: Equal Opportunities in Education","datePublished":"2025-07-22T12:51:50+03:00","dateModified":"2026-03-15T21:52:43+03:00","isPartOf":{"@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/#website"},"primaryImageOfPage":{"@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/ozyegin-universitesi-scholarship-tours.webp"},"inLanguage":"en-US"},{"@type":"Person","@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/en/author/murat/","name":"Murat","url":"https://roadtostudy.com/en/author/murat/","image":{"@type":"ImageObject","@id":"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/9f5b866231ae7aed7a61015846c1f0ab6c5797b065ec200b93c5e9daa87897af?s=96&amp;d=mm&amp;r=g","url":"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/9f5b866231ae7aed7a61015846c1f0ab6c5797b065ec200b93c5e9daa87897af?s=96&amp;d=mm&amp;r=g","caption":"Murat","inLanguage":"en-US"}},{"@type":"BlogPosting","headline":"Ozyegin University 2025: Equal Opportunities in Education","keywords":"Özyeğin University,Education,Equal Opportunity","datePublished":"2025-07-22T12:51:50+03:00","dateModified":"2026-03-15T21:52:43+03:00","articleSection":"University and Programs","author":{"@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/en/author/murat/","name":"Murat"},"publisher":{"@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/#person"},"description":"Özyeğin University offers full support to its students with the education opportunity equality scholarship. Learn the details and secure your future!","name":"Ozyegin University 2025: Equal Opportunities in Education","@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/en/ozyegin-equal-opportunity-in-education/#richSnippet","isPartOf":{"@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/en/ozyegin-equal-opportunity-in-education/#webpage"},"image":{"@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/ozyegin-universitesi-scholarship-tours.webp"},"inLanguage":"en-US","mainEntityOfPage":{"@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/en/ozyegin-equal-opportunity-in-education/#webpage"}}]}]}', "content_html" = '<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="what-does-equal-opportunity-in-education-mean">What Does Equal Opportunity in Education Mean?</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Everyone should have access to quality education, regardless of their social, economic or cultural background. In Turkey, this concept is often seen as ideal, but in practice, inequalities can occur. This is where the role of universities becomes critical.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Özyeğin University is one of the few institutions that has taken on this responsibility. Through both scholarships and student support mechanisms, it has put equal opportunity in education into practice in real terms. According to <a class="" href="https://www.unesco.org/en/education" target="_blank" rel="noopener">UNESCO reports</a>, such structural support contributes to social development in the long term.</p>


<div class="wp-block-spacer" style="height: 23px;" aria-hidden="true"> </div>
<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity" />
<div class="wp-block-spacer" style="height: 23px;" aria-hidden="true"> </div>


<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="how-is-equal-opportunity-provided-at-ozyegin-university">How is Equal Opportunity Provided at Ozyegin University?</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">At Ozyegin University, equal opportunity in education is not just a discourse; it is an approach that is supported by concrete steps. This university provides support to students not only on the basis of academic achievement, but also on the basis of needs.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">This program paves the way for young people who are deprived of the right to education due to financial constraints. Expenses such as tuition, dormitory, food, books and transportation are fully covered. In this context, the university makes equal opportunity in education not only theoretical but also a liveable experience.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">In addition, students do not lose their scholarships even in case of academic failure. I think this makes a huge difference. Because most of the time, the pressure on students is not success, but the fear of losing. This system of Özyeğin University makes equality of opportunity in education sustainable.</p>


<div style="height:23px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity" >
<div style="height:23px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>


<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="egitimde-firsat-esitligi-scholarship-program-details">Eğitimde Fırsat Eşitligi Scholarship Program Details</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">This scholarship program offered by Ozyegin University is a truly comprehensive and exemplary system. In this way, students who are successful but need financial support are admitted to the university with full scholarships.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">The scope of the scholarship is quite broad. Students do not pay tuition fees, stay in dormitories for free and receive cash support every month. This support is provided regularly for 9 months and aims to cover needs such as books, transportation and food. In other words, it is not limited to just entering the school gate, it covers the whole educational life of the student.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">The scholarship period can be extended up to 6 years with the preparatory class. Students pursuing a double major are also granted additional time. One of the most impressive aspects of the program is that the scholarships are free of charge. No compulsory service, no reimbursement&#8230; Fully focused on supporting the student.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Another reflection of the principle of equal opportunity in education is that scholarship recipients are not put under pressure based on academic performance. Of course, attendance and discipline are important, but no one feels like they are studying for fear of losing the scholarship.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">For more information about the program, you can also check out <a class="" href="https://ozuburs.ozyegin.edu.tr" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Equality of Opportunity in Education Scholarship Program</a>.</p>


<div style="height:23px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity" >
<div style="height:23px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>


<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="support-mechanisms-housing-food-and-more">Support Mechanisms: Housing, Food and More</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph"><a href="https://roadtostudy.com/ozyegin-universitesi-tanitim-rehberi/">Özyeğin University&#8217;s</a> understanding of equal opportunity in education is not limited to scholarships. What makes the real difference is that all the needs of students during their university life are taken into consideration. Scholarship recipients stay free of charge in university dormitories. In other words, for students coming from out of town, this means the elimination of a serious financial burden.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Food support is also very important. The university helps students meet their nutritional needs with monthly cash support. Moreover, the same support applies not only for food, but also for books, transportation, etc. This system embodies the principle of equal opportunity in education: every student can focus solely on their studies.</p>


<div style="height:23px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity" >
<div style="height:23px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>


<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="scholarship-application-process-and-who-can-benefit">Scholarship Application Process and Who Can Benefit?</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Who can benefit from this support? The application process for the Equal Opportunity in Education Scholarship is transparent and the applicant&#8217;s success and financial need are evaluated together. Özyeğin University aims to provide this scholarship every year to young people who are in real need, not just based on exam success.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">To apply for a scholarship, you fill out a form on the university&#8217;s online platform. Applications are usually received during the ÖSYS preference period. Scholarship candidates declare their need with documents and their academic performance is also taken into account.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Equality of opportunity in education takes center stage here again. Because a student&#8217;s potential is not only measured by points; living conditions and opportunities are also taken into account. Thanks to this scholarship, the dream of university is no longer a luxury, but an achievable goal.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">In addition, students who are accepted as scholarship recipients do not lose their scholarships even if they transfer. This is an indication of the university&#8217;s trust in students.</p>


<div style="height:23px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity" >
<div style="height:23px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>


<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="equality-of-opportunity-in-education-is-not-just-a-scholarship-but-a-future">Equality of Opportunity in Education is Not Just a Scholarship, but a Future</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">The Equal Opportunity in Education Scholarship Program offered by Ozyegin University is a unique system in Turkey. This approach, which enables students to access university without financial constraints, creates a real transformation. in this way, young people not only survive, but also take steps towards realizing their dreams.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">If you want to learn more about this scholarship program or prepare for the application process, you can check our <a href="https://roadtostudy.com" data-type="link" data-id="https://roadtostudy.com">Road to Study blog</a> and <a href="https://ozuburs.ozyegin.edu.tr" data-type="link" data-id="https://ozuburs.ozyegin.edu.tr" target="_blank" rel="noopener">university scholarship details</a>. The future starts with you. Now is the time to step up.</p>', "wp_published_at" = '2025-07-22T09:51:50Z', "wp_modified_at" = '2026-03-15T18:52:43Z', "featured_image" = '{"provider":"external","src":"/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/ozyegin-universitesi-scholarship-tours.webp","alt":"Types of scholarships offered at Özyeğin University","title":"ozyegin-universitesi-scholarship-tours"}' WHERE "deleted_at" IS NULL AND "status" = 'published' AND "locale" = 'en' AND "slug" = 'ozyegin-equal-opportunity-in-education';
