<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="terms-and-conditions">Terms and Conditions</h3>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li>Scholarships are awarded based on merit, potential and financial need.</li>



<li>The annual fee is paid in two equal installments.</li>



<li>The entrance scholarship also applies to the summer school and preparatory program.</li>
</ul>


