<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="campus-life-and-international-student-experience">Campus Life and International Student Experience</h2>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="cekmekoy-campus">Çekmeköy Campus</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">The modern campus in Istanbul, surrounded by nature, meets the needs of students not only academically but also socially. Campus life is vibrant with clubs, competitions and career events.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="advantages-for-international-students">Advantages for International Students</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph"> Özyeğin University has many support mechanisms for international students. Services such as the visa process, residence permits, and English-language academic advising are all clearly outlined on the <a href="https://www.ozyegin.edu.tr/en/international" target="_blank" rel="noopener">official international students page</a>. In addition, special events and communities have been created for the social cohesion of students from different cultures.</p>


<blockquote class="wp-block-quote">


<p class="wp-block-paragraph">For more information about our students&#8217; experiences, visit our <a class="" href="https://roadtostudy.com">guide to campus life</a>.</p>


</blockquote>
<div style="height:23px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity" >
<div style="height:23px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>


<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="shape-your-future-with-ozu">Shape Your Future with OzU!</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Özyeğin University is not just an educational institution; it is an ecosystem that prepares you for the international business world. With English-language education, a modern campus, a strong scholarship system and a hands-on curriculum, studying engineering at OzU is a serious privilege.</p>


<p><strong>If you want to be one of the engineers of the future</strong>, contact <a class="" href="https://roadtostudy.com">RoadToStudy counselors</a></p>


<p class="wp-block-paragraph">and start the application process easily!</p>



