<p class="wp-block-paragraph"><strong>Ozyeğin campus</strong> life offers not just classes but a complete experience for international students who want to study in Turkey. With two different campuses in Istanbul, Özyeğin University offers both an academic environment surrounded by nature and close access to the city center. In this article, you can find detailed information about <strong>özyeğin university çeköy</strong> and <strong>özyeğin university altunizade campus</strong>, as well as important details such as location, transportation and social life.</p>



<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="get-to-know-the-campus-closer">Get to Know the Campus Closer</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Want to feel the campus atmosphere before you come to Ozyegin University? With <a class="" href="https://360.ozyegin.edu.tr/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">360° Virtual Campus Tour</a>


</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph"><strong>Ozyeğin University address</strong> information is as follows:<br><strong>Nişantepe Mah. Orman Sok. No: 34-36, 34794 Alemdağ, Çekmeköy, Istanbul.</strong></p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">This <strong>özyeğin campus</strong> is like a small city with dormitories, outdoor sports fields, walking paths, modern classrooms and laboratories. Programs such as Master of Business Administration with thesis and Doctorate in Business Administration are also conducted here. The calm structure of Çekmeköy increases the concentration of the student, that&#8217;s for sure.</p>


