<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="altunizade-campus-a-modern-spot-in-the-city">Altunizade Campus: A Modern Spot in the City</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">For those who want to take classes in a more central location, <strong>özyeğin University Altunizade Campus</strong> is the right address. Located in the heart of Üsküdar district, this campus is used especially for graduate programs for working professionals.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph"><strong>Address:</strong> Altunizade Mah. Kısıklı Caddesi, Sarkuysan-Ak Business Center No:4, Block 1, Interior Door No:2, Üsküdar, Istanbul, 34662.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">This <strong>özyeğin campus</strong> is located right in the middle of city life. It is easy to reach, the classrooms are modern and suitable for a professional environment. Especially Financial Engineering and similar programs are offered here.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Some courses are also taught at the Swissotel in Beşiktaş. This shows that Özyeğin offers integrated education in different parts of Istanbul.</p>


