<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="ozyegin-university-on-map-how-to-get-there">Ozyegin University on Map: How to get there</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">If you are coming from out of town or abroad, Google Maps will be your best friend.<br>By typing &#8220;<strong>özyeğin university location</strong>&#8221; you can see the street address, directions and public transportation options for both <strong>özyeğin university çeköy</strong> and <strong>özyeğin university altunizade campus</strong>.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Especially in the first week, follow these steps:</p>



<ol class="wp-block-list">
<li><strong>Save on Map:</strong> Mark both Özyeğin campus addresses as &#8220;Favorites&#8221; on Google Maps.</li>



<li><strong>Examine Routes in Advance:</strong> Check the transportation time before you go.</li>



<li><strong>Use Public Transportation Apps:</strong> Apps like IETT, Trafi or Moovit can save a lot of time in Istanbul transportation.</li>



<li><strong>Add +10 Minutes to Travel Time:</strong> The biggest rule in Istanbul: Traffic always takes 10 minutes more.</li>
</ol>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Be sure to check the <a href="https://www.ozyegin.edu.tr/tr/iletisim" target="_blank" rel="noopener">özyeğin campus transportation page</a> for transportation details, shuttle times and campus routes. The university regularly shares up-to-date information here.</p>


