</figure>


<p class="wp-block-paragraph">These fees are annual and do not remain fixed throughout the study period; the university may update them by 10-20% each year. However, the scholarship rate indicated at the time of admission remains fixed for the entire duration of the student&#8217;s studies.</p>



<h4 class="wp-block-heading" id="how-much-do-you-pay-with-scholarships">How much do you pay with scholarships?</h4>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li><strong>Full Scholarship</strong>: $0 (Free)</li>



<li><strong>50% Scholarship</strong>: $11,000</li>



<li><strong>Paid</strong> (without scholarship): $22,000</li>
</ul>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">These fees include laboratory use, academic advising, library access and some technical materials. Accommodation and meals are charged separately. Average dormitory prices are <strong>3,000-5,000 USD</strong> per year, and living expenses are around <strong>3,000 USD</strong>.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">When we consider the cost of education and living, we can easily say that it is a much more economical option compared to universities in Europe or America.</p>


<div style="height:23px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity" >
<div style="height:23px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>


<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="where-do-graduates-work-internship-and-career-opportunities">Where Do Graduates Work? Internship and Career Opportunities</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Speaking of careers: Özyeğin University has established a strong connection with the business world. Graduates work for major technology companies in Turkey as well as global companies such as Amazon, Google and Microsoft. Especially students with a good project track record and English communication skills start receiving job offers even before they graduate.</p>



<h4 class="wp-block-heading" id="internships-are-not-just-formalities">Internships Are Not Just Formalities</h4>



<ol class="wp-block-list">
<li>most students have direct contact with the industry from the first grade. Thanks to the university&#8217;s Career Center, students can do internships in companies such as Turkcell, Trendyol and Insider. The university also offers summer internships in countries such as Germany, the Netherlands and Poland through Erasmus+ programs.</li>
</ol>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">In the department, &#8220;graduation projects&#8221; are based entirely on real sectoral problems. Professors usually involve students in their own research topics and these projects can be turned into publications.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">If you are interested in entrepreneurship, OzU-X is for you. They offer support for technology-based business ideas to meet with investors, build teams and even develop prototypes.</p>



