tostudy.com/#person"},"inLanguage":"en-US","mainEntityOfPage":{"@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/en/ozyegin-university-computer-engineering/#webpage"}}]}]}'), '$.content_html', '<figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-youtube wp-block-embed-youtube wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper">
<iframe loading="lazy" title="Aisha - Nigeria" width="720" height="405" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/FrD_69yeFgI?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe>
</div></figure>


<div class="wp-block-spacer" style="height: 31px;" aria-hidden="true"> </div>


<p class="wp-block-paragraph">A modern campus in the heart of Istanbul, but far away from the stress of the big city. In recent years, Özyeğin University has been attracting attention with its quality education in Computer Engineering and strong academic staff. Especially its research-oriented approach makes it an important center of attraction for international students. Let&#8217;s take a look at why you should choose this department.</p>


<div style="height:23px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity" >
<div style="height:23px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>


<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="why-ozyegin-university">Why Özyeğin University?</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">When I entered the campus for the first time, I honestly wasn&#8217;t expecting such a green and organized environment. Özyeğin University&#8217;s campus stands out with its modern architecture, but what is really fascinating is the university&#8217;s educational philosophy. There is a student-centered approach, meaning they really listen to you. The English-medium education and adaptation process for international students is well designed.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Everything from sports halls to design workshops, from student clubs to entrepreneurship centers has been considered on campus. In particular, the OzU-X entrepreneurship center provides a great advantage for students who want to produce projects in the field of technology and computer engineering.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">And most importantly: Academic staff. Many of the professors have PhDs abroad, contribute to scientific publications and are active in the sector.</p>


<div style="height:23px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity" >
<div style="height:23px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>


<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="how-is-the-computer-engineering-program">How is the Computer Engineering Program?</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">In this program, you learn not only how to code, but also the basics of computer science. The language of instruction is entirely in English, which prepares you for a global career. The program has a structure that balances theory and practice. From the first year, projects, laboratory applications and group work are intensively involved.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="deepening-education-with-broad-research-areas">Deepening Education with Broad Research Areas</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">The Computer Engineering department at Ozyegin University is really strong in research. Faculty members are actively conducting research in the following areas:</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph"><strong>Systems and Software:</strong> Projects are developed on fundamental topics such as cloud computing, data mining, data flows, service-oriented architectures, programming languages, software architecture and functional programming. This enables students to internalize both theoretical knowledge and practical application.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph"><strong>Machine Learning and Computer Vision:</strong> We are working on very current topics such as noise-insensitive speech recognition, text synthesis, 3D face modeling, video analysis and augmented reality. Including undergraduate students in these projects is a big plus.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph"><strong>Computer Networks:</strong> The focus is on wireless network technologies, next generation internet architectures and communication networks. Projects developed especially for the &#8220;internet of tomorrow&#8221; are supported by international collaborations.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">This diversity allows students to explore their own interests. When you graduate, you are not only a good engineer, but also a professional who knows which field he wants to specialize in.</p>


<div style="height:23px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity" >
<div style="height:23px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>


<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="ranking-of-ozyegin-university-in-2025">Ranking of Özyeğin University in 2025</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">According to the rankings, it is possible to see that Özyeğin University Computer Engineering department is on a serious rise. According to the 2024 placement results, the department accepts both students with high success rankings and a wider range of students thanks to the diversity of scholarships.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="2024-placement-table">2024 Placement Table</h3>



