<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="why-electrical-and-electronics-engineering-at-ozyegin-university">Why Electrical Electronics Engineering at Özyeğin University?</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Located on the Asian side of Istanbul, Özyeğin University has managed to become one of the most respected foundation universities in Turkey despite its young age. The Department of Electrical and Electronics Engineering is one of the most popular areas of the Faculty of Engineering. This department goes beyond classical lectures and offers students a <strong>practice-oriented engineering education</strong>.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">The campus atmosphere is dynamic, the laboratories are modern and the academics have both research and industry experience.</p>


<div style="height:23px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity" >
<div style="height:23px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>


