<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="elektrik-elektronik-engineering-syllabus">Elektrik-Elektronik Engineering Syllabus</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">The educational process covers both basic engineering knowledge and advanced technical expertise. Here are the main courses in the department:</p>



