</div>
<div class="wp-block-heading">
<h2 id="h-sikca-sorulan-sorular" class="wp-block-heading">Sıkça Sorulan Sorular</h2>
</div>
<div class="wp-block-paragraph">
<h3>Okul değiştirirken Türkiye’den çıkış yapmam gerekir mi?</h3>
<p>Hayır, genellikle sadece ikamet izni güncellemesi gerekir; ülke dışına çıkış yapmanız beklenmez. Ancak vize veya ikamet izninizin süresi dolmuşsa, çıkış-yeniden giriş gerekebilir.</p>
<h3>Okul değişikliği sırasında vize türüm değişir mi?</h3>
<p>Hayır, eğitim vizesi öğrencilik statüsünde yeterlidir. Yeni okuldan alınacak belgelerle ikamet izniniz güncellenir.</p>
<h3>Okul değişikliği bildirilmezse ne olur?</h3>
<p>İkamet izni iptal edilebilir; Türkiye’de yasal kalış statünüz kaybolabilir.</p>
<h3>İkamet izni başvurusu kaç günde sonuçlanır?</h3>
<p>Yoğunluk durumuna bağlı olarak değişiklik gösterse de, belgeleriniz eksiksizse genellikle birkaç hafta içerisinde sonuçlanır.</p>
<h3>Eğitim süresi boyunca ikamet iznini güncellemezsem ne olur?</h3>
<p>Mevcut ikamet izniniz geçerliliğini yitirir ve Türkiye&#8217;deki yasal statünüz tehlikeye girebilir.</p>
</div>', '$.wp_published_at', '2025-06-27T12:54:09Z', '$.wp_modified_at', '2026-03-15T18:53:35Z', '$.featured_image', json('{"provider":"external","src":"/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/criminal-records-documentation-for-foreigners.webp","alt":"Türkiye''de Okul Değiştirme Durumunda Vize ve İkamet İzni","title":"criminal-records-documentation-for-foreigners"}')) WHERE "collection" = 'posts' AND "id" = ( SELECT "live_revision_id" FROM "ec_posts" WHERE "deleted_at" IS NULL AND "status" = 'published' AND "locale" = 'tr' AND "slug" = 'okul-degistirme-vize-ikamet' );
UPDATE "ec_posts" SET "source_seo" = '{"title":"Career Support in Turkey: Make a Difference with Mentorship","description":"Shape your future with career support in Turkey. Discover mentorship, scholarship, and project opportunities! Take action now and create your roadmap.","robots":"follow, index, max-snippet:-1, max-video-preview:-1, max-image-preview:large","ogTitle":"Career Support in Turkey: Make a Difference with Mentorship","ogDescription":"Shape your future with career support in Turkey. Discover mentorship, scholarship, and project opportunities! Take action now and create your roadmap.","ogImage":"/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/specific-scholarship-programs-in-turkey-1-1024x772.webp","twitterCard":"summary_large_image","twitterTitle":"Career Support in Turkey: Make a Difference with Mentorship","twitterDescription":"Shape your future with career support in Turkey. Discover mentorship, scholarship, and project opportunities! Take action now and create your roadmap.","canonicalPath":"/en/career-support-in-turkey/","hreflang":[{"hreflang":"tr","href":"/turkiyede-kariyer-destekleri/"},{"hreflang":"en","href":"/en/career-support-in-turkey/"}],"jsonLd":[{"@context":"https://schema.org","@graph":[{"@type":["Organization","Person"],"@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/#person","name":"Road to Study - Turkey University Guide for Students","url":"https://roadtostudy.com","logo":{"@type":"ImageObject","@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/#logo","url":"https://roadtostudy.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Kare-Logo-e1740739634958.png","contentUrl":"https://roadtostudy.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Kare-Logo-e1740739634958.png","caption":"Road to Study - Turkey University Guide for Students","inLanguage":"en-US","width":"450","height":"445"},"image":{"@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/#logo"}},{"@type":"WebSite","@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/#website","url":"https://roadtostudy.com","name":"Road to Study - Turkey University Guide for Students","alternateName":"Road to Study in Turkey","publisher":{"@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/#person"},"inLanguage":"en-US"},{"@type":"ImageObject","@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/specific-scholarship-programs-in-turkey-1.webp","url":"https://roadtostudy.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/specific-scholarship-programs-in-turkey-1.webp","width":"2336","height":"1760","caption":"A mentor guiding a young professional during a career planning session in Turkiye.","inLanguage":"en-US"},{"@type":"WebPage","@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/en/career-support-in-turkey/#webpage","url":"https://roadtostudy.com/en/career-support-in-turkey/","name":"Career Support in Turkey: Make a Difference with Mentorship","datePublished":"2025-08-26T13:29:01+03:00","dateModified":"2026-03-15T21:45:16+03:00","isPartOf":{"@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/#website"},"primaryImageOfPage":{"@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/specific-scholarship-programs-in-turkey-1.webp"},"inLanguage":"en-US"},{"@type":"Person","@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/en/author/murat/","name":"Murat","url":"https://roadtostudy.com/en/author/murat/","image":{"@type":"ImageObject","@id":"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/9f5b866231ae7aed7a61015846c1f0ab6c5797b065ec200b93c5e9daa87897af?s=96&amp;d=mm&amp;r=g","url":"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/9f5b866231ae7aed7a61015846c1f0ab6c5797b065ec200b93c5e9daa87897af?s=96&amp;d=mm&amp;r=g","caption":"Murat","inLanguage":"en-US"}},{"@type":"BlogPosting","headline":"Career Support in Turkey: Make a Difference with Mentorship","keywords":"career support","datePublished":"2025-08-26T13:29:01+03:00","dateModified":"2026-03-15T21:45:16+03:00","articleSection":"Scholarships and Funding","author":{"@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/en/author/murat/","name":"Murat"},"publisher":{"@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/#person"},"description":"Shape your future with career support in Turkey. Discover mentorship, scholarship, and project opportunities! Take action now and create your roadmap.","name":"Career Support in Turkey: Make a Difference with Mentorship","@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/en/career-support-in-turkey/#richSnippet","isPartOf":{"@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/en/career-support-in-turkey/#webpage"},"image":{"@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/specific-scholarship-programs-in-turkey-1.webp"},"inLanguage":"en-US","mainEntityOfPage":{"@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/en/career-support-in-turkey/#webpage"}}]}]}', "content_html" = '<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="mentoring-programs-offered-at-universities">Mentoring Programs Offered at Universities</h2><p class="wp-block-paragraph"><strong>Career support in Turkey</strong> is not just about scholarships and job placements for international students; it also includes mentoring, project grants and academic development opportunities. If you are planning to study in Turkey or are already studying in Turkey, knowing these systems can give you a serious advantage. I can&#8217;t forget the confusion I experienced while researching all these supports in my first year; that&#8217;s why this article exists.</p><h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="2248-academic-guidance-with-mentoring-support-program">2248 Academic Guidance with Mentoring Support Program</h3><p class="wp-block-paragraph">The <a href="https://tubitak.gov.tr/tr/burslar/lisans-onlisans/mentorluk-destegi-programi/2248-mentorluk-destegi-programi" target="_blank" rel="noopener">2248 Mentorship Support Program</a> offered by TÜBİTAK is an important resource especially for graduate students. Through this program, students can work one-on-one with experienced academics and receive support in project development, publication preparation and academic networking. </p><h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="faculties-specific-student-mentoring-systems">Faculties Specific Student Mentoring Systems</h3><p class="wp-block-paragraph">Most universities in Turkey have established faculty-based mentoring systems. In fields such as engineering, health sciences and social sciences, first-year students are often paired with third- or fourth-year students to facilitate the university adaptation process. These systems provide guidance not only on course selection, but also on club activities, ways to find internships, etc.</p><div style="height:23px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div><hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity" ><div style="height:23px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div><h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="important-career-support-institutions-in-turkey">Important Career Support Institutions in Turkey</h2><p class="wp-block-paragraph">Career support for international students in Turkey is usually offered through university career centers and government-sponsored programs. However, it is very important to be aware of these supports and to follow the application processes. Especially <strong>TUBITAK</strong>, <strong>KOSGEB</strong> and some municipalities offer serious opportunities for young people.</p><h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="tubitak-3501-career-development-program">TUBITAK 3501 Career Development Program</h3><p class="wp-block-paragraph">Although TÜBİTAK&#8217;s 3501 Program is designed for young academics conducting postdoctoral research, graduate students can also indirectly benefit from the financial and mentoring support offered by the program. This program is one of the oldest career support programs in Turkey. Project support can be up to <strong>about 12,800 USD</strong>.</p><h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="kosgeb-and-young-entrepreneur-supports">KOSGEB and Young Entrepreneur Supports</h3><p class="wp-block-paragraph">The entrepreneurship grants provided by KOSGEB are an important opportunity for international students who want to realize their own business idea. Young entrepreneurs who apply and complete the trainings can receive business start-up support starting from <strong>25,000 TL</strong> (approximately <strong>640 USD</strong>) up to <strong>100,000 TL</strong> (<strong>2,560 USD</strong>).</p><div style="height:23px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div><hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity" ><div style="height:23px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div><h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="social-cultural-and-environmental-projects-in-turkey">Social, Cultural and Environmental Projects in Turkey</h2><p class="wp-block-paragraph">Career support in Turkey is not limited to the academic and business world. Thanks to the grants given to projects in areas such as social responsibility, cultural heritage and environment, students can also gain experience in the active field.</p><h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="financial-supports-for-social-responsibility-projects">Financial Supports for Social Responsibility Projects</h3><p class="wp-block-paragraph">Several times a year, the Ministry of Youth and Sports opens calls for support for social responsibility projects carried out in collaboration with university clubs. These grants provide a budget of <strong>5,000-20,000 TL</strong> (approximately <strong>130-510 USD</strong>) for projects such as providing books to children and organizing activities with people with disabilities.</p><h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="grants-for-cultural-heritage-and-conservation-works">Grants for Cultural Heritage and Conservation Works</h3><p class="wp-block-paragraph">Projects to protect cultural heritage are supported by the UNESCO National Commission for Turkey and some local municipalities. Funding is provided for both cultural content production and field research. These projects are a great opportunity for those who want to advance in the artistic field among career supports in Turkey.</p><h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="opportunities-for-environmental-and-sustainability-projects">Opportunities for Environmental and Sustainability Projects</h3><p class="wp-block-paragraph">Organizations such as the TEMA Foundation and ÇEVKO offer small grants and training to university students to develop projects on environmental awareness and sustainability. What starts as volunteer work can turn into a professional career path over time.</p><div style="height:23px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div><hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity" ><div style="height:23px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div><h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="supports-for-academic-and-scientific-projects-in-turkey">Supports for Academic and Scientific Projects in Turkey</h2><p class="wp-block-paragraph">Career support in Turkey is quite varied for international students who want to develop academic projects. Both state and private funds are available for fields such as science, technology, health and agriculture. In the process of producing projects, serious budgets are provided with mentoring.</p><h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="patent-and-intellectual-property-research">Patent and Intellectual Property Research</h3><p class="wp-block-paragraph">Thanks to technology transfer offices (TTOs) in Turkey, students have the chance to commercialize their inventions. Students who do <em><a href="https://roadtostudy.com/turkiye-patent-ve-fikri-mulkiyet-destekleri/" data-type="post" data-id="2843">intellectual property studies</a></em> are given financial support for patent applications through KOSGEB and TÜBİTAK. The average patent application cost is around <strong>7,000 TL</strong> (approximately <strong>180 USD</strong>). This kind of support is worth gold for innovation-oriented students within the scope of career support in Turkey.</p><h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="financing-in-educational-technologies-and-health">Financing in Educational Technologies and Health</h3><p class="wp-block-paragraph">TUSEB and some foundation universities offer laboratories and scholarships for health research. Technoparks are a starting point for students who want to develop educational technologies. Grants offered especially in the fields of IT, artificial intelligence and mobile application development range between <strong>10,000-50,000 TL</strong> (<strong>260-1,280 USD</strong>).</p><h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="incentives-provided-for-agriculture-food-and-energy-research">Incentives Provided for Agriculture, Food and Energy Research</h3><p class="wp-block-paragraph">R&amp;D projects carried out in cooperation with the Ministry of Agriculture are supported for students who want to make use of Turkey&#8217;s agricultural potential. Issues such as food security, sustainable energy, efficient use of water resources are among the topics that are becoming increasingly important in career support in Turkey.</p><p class="wp-block-paragraph">Interested students can develop projects in these areas and receive support from TÜBİTAK, Chambers of Agriculture and private organizations.</p><div style="height:23px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div><hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity" ><div style="height:23px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div><h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="scholarship-support-and-financial-planning-guide-in-turkey">Scholarship Support and Financial Planning Guide in Turkey</h2><p class="wp-block-paragraph">Scholarships are one of the first things that come to mind when it comes to career support in Turkey. Both government and university scholarships are available for international students. However, this process needs to be well planned and the right application must be made.</p><h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="points-to-consider-in-scholarship-applications">Points to Consider in Scholarship Applications</h3><p class="wp-block-paragraph">Each scholarship program has different criteria. Some focus on academic achievement, while others are based on financial need. Applications are usually received via e-government, YÖK or universities&#8217; own portals. It is very important that the documents are complete.</p><h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="motivation-letter-and-reference-processes">Motivation Letter and Reference Processes</h3><p class="wp-block-paragraph">The motivational letter is one of the most critical points in the process of winning a scholarship. Instead of clichés, you need to tell your story and clarify your goals. Reference letters should be from academic professors. <a href="https://roadtostudy.com/turkiye-bursu-icin-motivasyon-mektubu/" data-type="post" data-id="2885">Road to Study&#8217;s motivation letter preparation guide</a> can guide you in this regard.</p><h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="academic-cv-preparation-and-interview-tips">Academic CV Preparation and Interview Tips</h3><p class="wp-block-paragraph">Academic CV is one of the most frequently requested documents for career support in Turkey. Your projects, seminars and volunteering activities should be included in detail. Interviews are usually conducted online. A clear, open and reassuring communication style works well.</p><h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="comparison-of-scholarship-and-loan-systems-in-turkey">Comparison of Scholarship and Loan Systems in Turkey</h3><p class="wp-block-paragraph">State scholarships are free of charge, while student loans require repayment. It is important to understand this difference well. The KYK scholarship provides a monthly support of <strong>2,000 TL</strong> (approximately <strong>51 USD</strong>), while the loan option is the same amount and is repaid after graduation. This is the most accessible career support in Turkey, but it is important to know the pros and cons of both options.</p><div style="height:23px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div><hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity" ><div style="height:23px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div><h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="shape-your-future-in-turkey-step-up-now">Shape Your Future in Turkey: Step Up Now!</h2><p class="wp-block-paragraph">Career support for international students in Turkey is not only available at school, but in all aspects of life. By doing research, making the right connections and participating in projects, you can forge a unique path for yourself. Whether you have academic goals or entrepreneurial plans, you are more likely to find support in this country than you think.</p><p>The time to invest in yourself is now. If you don&#8217;t know where to start, you can take the first step with the counseling and guidance services offered by <a class="" href="https://roadtostudy.com">Road to Study</a><p class="wp-block-paragraph">. Take action now to learn more about career support in Turkey and chart your own path!</p>', "wp_published_at" = '2025-08-26T10:29:01Z', "wp_modified_at" = '2026-03-15T18:45:16Z', "featured_image" = '{"provider":"external","src":"/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/specific-scholarship-programs-in-turkey-1.webp","alt":"A mentor guiding a young professional during a career planning session in Turkiye.","title":"specific-scholarship-programs-in-turkey"}' WHERE "deleted_at" IS NULL AND "status" = 'published' AND "locale" = 'en' AND "slug" = 'career-support-in-turkey';
