":"https://roadtostudy.com/en/author/murat/","name":"Murat"},"@type":"BlogPosting","name":"Özyeğin University Industrial Engineering - RoadtoStudy","articleSection":"University and Programs","@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/en/ozyegin-university-industrial-engineering/#schema-11437","isPartOf":{"@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/en/ozyegin-university-industrial-engineering/#webpage"},"publisher":{"@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/#person"},"inLanguage":"en-US","mainEntityOfPage":{"@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/en/ozyegin-university-industrial-engineering/#webpage"}},{"@type":"VideoObject","name":"Özyeğin University Industrial Engineering - RoadtoStudy","description":"Enjoy the videos and music you love, upload original content, and share it all with friends, family, and the world on YouTube.","uploadDate":"2025-07-23T11:23:31+03:00","thumbnailUrl":"https://roadtostudy.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/ozyegin-university-industrial-engineering.webp","embedUrl":"https://www.youtube.com/embed/XTYVdDIcLTU","isFamilyFriendly":"True","@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/en/ozyegin-university-industrial-engineering/#schema-11438","isPartOf":{"@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/en/ozyegin-university-industrial-engineering/#webpage"},"publisher":{"@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/#person"},"inLanguage":"en-US","mainEntityOfPage":{"@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/en/ozyegin-university-industrial-engineering/#webpage"}}]}]}', "content_html" = '<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Choosing a university is not easy, especially if you are going to study abroad. Which city? Which university? Which department? I was in the middle of these questions, and I was quite confused at the time. Especially in technical departments like engineering, it is essential to consider quality, vision and job opportunities together. This is exactly why Özyeğin University&#8217;s Department of Industrial Engineering stands out. The department, which has been providing education since 2009, stands out with both theoretical and practical aspects.</p>



