</div></figure>


<div style="height:23px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity" >
<div style="height:23px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>


<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="ozyegin-university-foreign-student-fees-2025-2026">Özyeğin University Foreign Student Fees 2025-2026</h2>


<figure class="wp-block-table">
<table class="has-fixed-layout">
<thead>
<tr>
<th>Scholarship Type</th>
<th>Annual Fee (USD)</th>
<th>Description</th>
</tr>
</thead>
<thead>
<tbody>
<tr>
<td><strong>Full Scholarship</strong></td>
<td>0</td>
<td>The education is completely free. Food/housing scholarship can also be added.</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td><strong>50% Scholarship</strong></td>
<td>11,000</td>
<td>Half the normal fee.</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td><strong>Fee</strong></td>
<td>22,000</td>
<td>Full fee for non-scholarship students.</td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</figure>


<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Our faculty members award academic merit-based entrance scholarships based on the information you provide during the application evaluation process. For detailed information on scholarships, click here: <a href="https://studentservices.ozyegin.edu.tr/tr/burs-ve-finansal-destek" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Scholarship Terms and Conditions.</a></p>


<div style="height:23px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity" >
<div style="height:23px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>


<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="ozyegin-university-industrial-engineering-application-requirements">Özyegin University Industrial Engineering Application Requirements</h2>



<h4 class="wp-block-heading" id="documents-required-for-international-students">Documents Required for International Students</h4>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Özyeğin University offers a special admission process for international students. The following documents are required to apply:<br>&#8211; High school diploma (English or Turkish translation)<br>&#8211; Transcript<br>&#8211; Copy of passport<br>&#8211; Letter of motivation<br>&#8211; IELTS, TOEFL or equivalent English proficiency certificate<br>&#8211; SAT, ACT, IB or country-specific exam results (for some programs)</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">If you are entering Turkey on a student visa, be sure to check out <strong><a href="http://roadtostudy.com" data-type="link" data-id="roadtostudy.com">Entering Turkey on a Student Visa: Be sure to check our </a><a></a></strong><a>Airport Procedures</a> article. Don&#8217;t be caught off guard by the procedures you may encounter at the airport.</p>


<div style="height:23px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity" >
<div style="height:23px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>


<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="industrial-engineering-course-content-not-just-math">Industrial Engineering Course Content: Not Just Math</h2>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="compulsory-and-elective-courses">Compulsory and Elective Courses</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">In addition to classical engineering courses, the program is also supported by social sciences. In the first years, basic engineering courses such as calculus, physics and linear algebra are taken. In the following years, business analytics, production systems, supply chain and optimization courses come into play.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">If you want to review the full syllabus, you can take a look at the officially published <strong><a class="" href="https://www.ozyegin.edu.tr/pdfviewer/muhendislik-2023-2024.php" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Özyeğin University Faculty of Engineering 2023-2024 Syllabus PDF</a></strong>. Here you can see both the semester courses and their contents in detail.</p>



<h4 class="wp-block-heading" id="project-based-education-and-laboratory-experience">Project-Based Education and Laboratory Experience</h4>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Students do not only receive theoretical knowledge. Thanks to the project-based education model, each student is encouraged to produce a solution to a real problem. Özyeğin&#8217;s laboratories and software infrastructure are very strong in this regard.</p>


<div style="height:23px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity" >
<div style="height:23px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>


<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="industrial-engineering-ranking-at-ozyegin">Industrial Engineering Ranking at Ozyegin</h3>



<figure class="wp-block-table"><table class="has-fixed-layout"><thead><tr><th><strong>Scholarship Type</strong></th><th><strong>Quota</strong></th><th><strong>Minimum Score</strong></th><th><strong>Maximum Score</strong></th><th><strong>Minimum Ranking</strong></th><th><strong>Maximum Ranking</strong></th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>Full Scholarship</td><td>14</td><td>512.67974</td><td>529.84771</td><td>6,205</td><td>2,306</td></tr><tr><td>50% Scholarship</td><td>49</td><td>402.92892</td><td>491.42601</td><td>79,550</td><td>14,004</td></tr><tr><td>Paid (No Scholarship)</td><td>44*</td><td>336.41552</td><td>402.02033</td><td>172,599</td><td>80,538</td></tr></tbody></table></figure>



<h4 class="wp-block-heading" id="university-accreditations-and-academic-achievements">University Accreditations and Academic Achievements</h4>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">The department, which was included in the MÜDEK (Association for Evaluation and Accreditation of Engineering Education Programs) process in 2014, offers an internationally recognized program. This accreditation increases both the quality of education and the chances of finding a job.</p>


<div style="height:23px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity" >
<div style="height:23px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>


<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="programs-that-an-industrial-engineer-should-know">Programs that an industrial engineer should know</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">When we say industrial engineering, it is not only about dealing with numbers; it is also necessary to know the tools that will make those numbers meaningful. </p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="more-than-python-matlab-and-excel">More Than Python, MATLAB and Excel</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Özyeğin University&#8217;s Industrial Engineering program aims to provide students with competence in different software languages and systems. In particular, the following software is integrated into various courses of the program:</p>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li><strong>Python</strong>: Data analysis, optimization algorithms, machine learning basics</li>



<li><strong>MATLAB</strong>: Engineering calculations, system modeling</li>



<li><strong>Excel + VBA</strong>: Frequently used in operational decision-making</li>



<li><strong>Arena/Simul8</strong>: For simulation-based system modeling</li>



<li><strong>GAMS / CPLEX / LINGO</strong>: In solving optimization problems</li>
</ul>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">When you graduate, you will be able to apply these tools. So you won&#8217;t just &#8220;hear about it&#8221;; you will actually produce a project.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="how-software-education-is-provided-at-ozyegin">How Software Education is Provided at Ozyegin?</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">The courses emphasize not only theoretical knowledge but also practical application. For example, you integrate the formula you learned in an optimization course into a logistics simulation and analyze it with software. Team projects, individual assignments and final exams help you transfer your technical skills to real life.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Moreover, these programs are not taught in isolation; they are all shown as a means of solving a problem. So while you are learning software, you are actually developing your problem solving muscles.</p>



<h4 class="wp-block-heading" id="technical-competencies-that-will-make-a-difference-in-cv">Technical Competencies That Will Make a Difference in CV</h4>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">As an industrial engineer graduating from Ozyeğin, you won&#8217;t just have a diploma. Among the hundreds of CVs that say &#8220;I use Excel well&#8221;, it is clear that someone who has done production optimization with Python will make a difference. This software knowledge is not a plus for your career, it is a necessity. Özyeğin offers you this infrastructure in a systematic way.</p>


<div style="height:23px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity" >
<div style="height:23px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>


<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="where-do-ozyegin-industrial-engineering-graduates-work">Where do Ozyegin Industrial Engineering Graduates Work?</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">When we are students, we all ask ourselves the same question: &#8220;Will I be able to find a job after graduating from this department?&#8221; I understand this concern very well because I used to check LinkedIn more often as graduation approached. Fortunately for Özyeğin Industrial Engineering graduates, this question usually ends with a positive answer.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="career-opportunities-in-global-and-local-companies">Career Opportunities in Global and Local Companies</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Özyeğin graduates can find jobs in large companies both in Turkey and abroad. The department prepares its students particularly strongly in <strong>supply chain, production planning, logistics and process management</strong>. Here are some of the companies where graduates work:</p>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li><strong>Unilever</strong></li>



<li><strong>Procter &amp; Gamble (P&amp;G)</strong></li>



<li><strong>Amazon</strong></li>



<li><strong>Ford Otosan</strong></li>



<li><strong>Turkish Airlines</strong></li>



<li><strong>Arçelik</strong></li>



<li><strong>McKinsey &amp; Company</strong></li>
</ul>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Graduates do not only turn to the private sector. A strong groundwork is also being prepared for those aiming for an academic career. Many students receive acceptance from universities in Europe and America for post-graduate master&#8217;s or doctoral studies.</p>


<div style="height:23px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity" >
<div style="height:23px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>


<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="start-today-for-your-future-becoming-an-engineer-at-ozyegin">Start Today for Your Future: Becoming an Engineer at Özyeğin</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">University education is not just a four-year period; it is the years that determine who you are and what you become. If you like analytical thinking, building systems and solving problems, industrial engineering might be the right choice for you. And it is a great advantage to receive this education at Özyeğin, <strong>one of the most innovative universities</strong> in Istanbul, which is closest to technology.</p>



<h4 class="wp-block-heading" id="why-ozyegin-student-life-and-scholarship-opportunities">Why Özyeğin? Student Life and Scholarship Opportunities</h4>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph"> Özyeğin offers a lot not only academically but also in terms of campus life. Clubs, hackathons, social responsibility projects, student leadership opportunities&#8230; As an engineering student, you learn not only how to code, but also how to manage a team and make effective presentations. And of course the scholarship system is very accessible: One out of every two students receives a 50% scholarship. Full scholarships are also available.</p>



<h4 class="wp-block-heading" id="start-your-application-now-dont-miss-opportunities">Start Your Application Now, Don&#8217;t Miss Opportunities</h4>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">If Özyeğin University&#8217;s Industrial Engineering program appeals to you, now is the time to take the plunge. The application process is online and very user-friendly. <a class="" href="https://roadtostudy.com">Road to Study</a> offers both an application guide and one-on-one counseling.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Don&#8217;t wait any longer to build your dream career. Start today, design your future.</p>



